title: Vismeh
text: Vismeh (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as Vīsmeh) is a village in <a href="Davudabad%20Rural%20District">Davudabad Rural District</a>, in the <a href="Central%20District%20%28Arak%20County%29">Central District</a> of <a href="Arak%20County">Arak County</a>, <a href="Markazi%20Province">Markazi Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 594, in 185 families.
